# AXIOM ACTIVITY LOG — Run [RUN_ID]
# ============================================================
# Format:  [TAG] YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ | Persona | Description | Refs
# Rules:   Append-only. Never edit existing lines.
#          Corrections → new [CORRECTION] line.
#          Commit this file with every significant git commit.
#          This is the FIRST file to read when orienting after a session drop.
# ============================================================
# Tags:
#   [INIT]        Run initialised
#   [START]       Ticket / sub-task started
#   [DONE]        Ticket / sub-task completed
#   [HANDOVER]    Handover posted (Jira + HANDOVERS.md)
#   [CHECKPOINT]  State snapshot — written after every HANDOVER. Read this to recover.
#                 Format: Phase: X | Done: Y | Next: Z | Blockers: None/description
#                 Recovery: grep "\[CHECKPOINT\]" ACTIVITY.log | tail -1
#   [BLOCKER]     Blocker raised
#   [UNBLOCK]     Blocker resolved
#   [DECISION]    Decision recorded in DECISIONS.md
#   [COMMIT]      Significant git commit
#   [DEPLOY]      Successful npm run deploy
#   [VALIDATE]    Casey test result
#   [SCOPE]       Scope change approved
#   [MILESTONE]   Phase transition or hour checkpoint
#   [SUBMIT]      Submission action
#   [CORRECTION]  Correction to a prior line
# ============================================================

